overview: This is Ibiza film will take you on a tour to one of the most infamous islands in the entire world where extraordinary mix of night-life hedonism and spiritual evolution create a unique culture of dance, music and love.
tagline: Former resident and all-around Ibiza enthusiast, actor/host Jermaine Whitehead Bailey will show you the side everyone's favorite "White Isle" that doesn't make the typical tour guide.
title: This is Ibiza
